{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_74","type":"agent_message","text":"The root cause is clearer now. `hadoopConfiguration()` only sets one flag and relies on Hadoop defaults; in the native image those defaults are incomplete, so `AvroSequenceFile.addToConfiguration` overwrites `io.serializations` with only the Avro serializer. I’m checking how this repo handles `core-default.xml`/Hadoop default resources before patching the metadata."}}
